    "logo": "",
    "description": "R Veterinary at Columbia is a premier veterinary care located in 400 Nebraska Ave, Columbia, MO 65201, USA. we specialize in Pet care, Professional services, Indoor facilities. Our indoor facilities provide a safe, climate-controlled environment for your beloved pets. Our experienced and caring staff ensures that every pet receives personalized attention and care. Contact us at (573) 443-7274 to schedule a visit or learn more about our services. Visit our website at https://www.r.vet/columbia for detailed information about our facilities and pricing. We welcome you to bring your furry friend and experience the difference that professional pet care makes.",
